          illustration of the VT-100 keypad, and the keystrokes that are
          required in order to emulate the respective key.  The keypad layout
          and functionality should be familiar to VT-100 users.

                        +--------+--------+--------+--------+
                        |        |        | Shift- | Shift- |
                        |   F1   |   F2   |   F1   |   F2   |
                        |        |        |        |        |
                        +--------+--------+--------+--------+
                        |        |        | Shift- | Shift- |
                        |   F3   |   F4   |   F3   |   F4   |
                        |        |        |        |        |
                        +--------+--------+--------+--------+
