                        +--------+--------+--------+--------+
                        |        |        | Shift- |        |
                        |   F7   |   F8   |   F7   |        |
                        |        |        |        | Shift- |
                        +--------+--------+--------+   F10  |
                        |                 | Shift- |        |
                        |       F10       |   F9   |        |
                        |                 |        |        |
